                            Summary on Grant Application Form</td>
		</tr>
		<tr>
			<td colspan="6" class="DetailValue" style="padding:5px;">
                        <span id="lblAbstract">The Interim Report of the joint government/Industry review of procurement and contractual arrangement in the UK Construction Industry headed by Sir Michael Lotham suggest multi attribute contractor selection.  Incidentally a new methodology being developed by the applicant seems to meet the aspirations of the review panel with a 3-stage approach to contractor selection.  The research herein proposed seeks to validate this methodology and will shed more light on the nature, importance and interdependencies between the contractor selection variables.</span>
                        </td>
